{"tid":1534413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[運動新方向]策略上,我地應該鼓勵林鄭造反,分化林鄭同中共","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:50:39.000Z","uid":38991,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6c31cb2fd2f67b3ff98d56652611ddbe5042a9","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"錄音流出之後真相大白<br />\n1. 林鄭好想辭職但走唔到<br />\n2. 5大訴求係中共唔批<br />\n<br />\n而事實上, 如果林鄭夠勇氣, 佢可以先斬後奏,做完5大訴求然後公開辭職,但係呢一刻佢仲唔敢,因為佢而家係香港已經係過街老鼠,擔心做完會比中共清算但係香港人又唔企係佢個邊(睇下曾蔭權下場)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n實際上有咩可以做呢, 學返中共, 一手硬一手軟<br />\n<br />\n1. 國際層面, 林鄭有份破壞中英聯合聲明, 一國兩制(有埋錄音證明啦), 搵英美議員要求制裁林鄭一家人, 等佢造唔造反都比人清算<br />\n<br />\n2. 本地層面, 公開呼籲林鄭企返係香港人呢邊, 可以攪場遊行支持佢轉做污點證人, 動之以情其實香港人仲好支持你架 (扮下野)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1dac967c5a3af340a84254409bb35a198ca134","tid":1534413,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:53:49.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span>"},{"pid":"38fcc32a86d5d3495f53c98d5050bdbf727db338","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:54:00.000Z","msg":"又要自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb139accca1cf4442ca0aa32fff818c39d5a4fd","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"又要自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5f04bbf1518d481083d5c12c317efa9e569fbd","tid":1534413,"uid":204205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03c51c41f23d308240becb190572ebf94d57cfca","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50fcf09b1cc3a2441be0247558b3602d0f37792e","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8a1da395e40ae64bcb985264823c167b7a9c7ff","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5d220f02b18bfb32bb4bf0d87452681ae21a97","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b4c46e98bfe61880169f20a10b45ac7e3b2374a","tid":1534413,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"一做五大訴求班狗應該會去打鳩林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e2dff33b8cf15cd4c1bdb180fbfdf311aea32c","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b4c46e98bfe61880169f20a10b45ac7e3b2374a","tid":1534413,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"一做五大訴求班狗應該會去打鳩林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c