立場"},{"pid":"1f3a7864f758754fb20f6ac0801fd80b0e3fe06f","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6153b196b8764fdae1af7d847eda5365e575f7e","tid":1534413,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:19:59.000Z","msg":"佢唔敢<br />\n權威性人格   欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"75056f81f957fd0f648ee78ea3a4874e835d37c6","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2739788b9b781ee64d7947089b64073b0bdc1f55","tid":1534413,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d1e3381b69f0f3a376cc79fd9b30aafa43fee0","tid":1534413,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"}]}